quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  60,1,momino! agar tum meri raah mein larnay aur meri khushnodi talab karne ke liye ( mukkay se ) niklay ho to mere aur apne dushmanon ko dost nah banaao. tum to un ko dosti ke pegham bhaijtay ho aur woh ( deen ) haq se jo tumahray paas aaya hai munhkir hain. aur is baais se ke tum apne perwar-digaar khuda taala par imaan laaye ho paighambar ko aur tum ko jalaa-watan karte hain. tum un ki taraf posheeda posheeda dosti ke pegham bhaijtay ho. aur jo kuch tum makhfi tor par aur jo Ali al-elaan karte ho woh mujhe maloom hai. aur jo koi tum mein se aisa kere ga woh seedhay rastay se bhatak gaya
  60,2,agar yeh kafir tum par qudrat paleen to tumahray dushman ho jaien aur aeza ke liye tum par haath ( bhi ) chalayein aur zubanain ( bhi ) aur chahtay hain ke tum kisi terhan kafir hojao
  60,3,qayamat ke din nah tumahray rishte naatay kaam ayen ge aur nah aulaad. is roz wohi tum mein faisla kere ga. aur jo kuch tum karte ho khuda is ko daikhta hai
  60,4,tumhe ibrahim aur un ke رفقاء ki naik chaal chalni ( zaroor ) hai. jab unhon ne apni qoum ke logon se kaha ke hum tum se aur un ( buton ) se jin ko tum khuda ke siwa pujte ho be talluq hain ( aur ) tumahray ( mabodon ke kabhi ) qaail nahi ( ho saktay ) aur jab taq tum khuday-e wahid aur imaan nah lao hum mein tum mein hamesha khullam khula adawat aur dushmani rahay gi. haan ibrahim ne apne baap se yeh ( zaroor ) kaha ke mein aap ke liye mughfirat maanguu ga aur khuda ke samnay aap ke baray mein kisi cheez ka kuch ikhtiyar nahi rakhta. ae hamaray perwar-digaar tujh hi par hamara bharosa hai aur teri hi taraf hum rujoo karte hain aur tairay hi huzoor mein ( hamein ) lout kar aana hai
  60,5,ae hamaray perwar-digaar hum ko kafiroon ke haath se azaab nah dilana aur ae perwar-digaar hamaray hamein maaf farma. be shak to ghalib hikmat wala hai
